macandrews & forbes inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Private Equity
MacAndrews & Forbes Incorporated operates as a private equity firm. The Company invests in consumer products, banking, media, e-commerce, life sciences, entertainment, cosmetics, security, and biotechnology industries.




