July 26, 2017 7:35 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of MacAndrews & Forbes Holdings, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
MacAndrews and Forbes Holdings Inc. is a principal investment firm specializing in investments in the retail sector. The firm prefers to make investments in companies engaged in the consumer products, banking, media, e-commerce, life sciences, entertainment, cosmetics, security, and biotechnology industries. It was formerly known as Mafco Holdings. MacAndrews & Forbes Holdings, Inc. was founded in 1991 and is based in New York, New York.


35 East 62nd StreetNew York, NY 10065United StatesFounded in 1991



Phone: 212-572-8600

www.macandrewsandforbes.com







