MacAndrews & Forbes Holdings, Inc. Key Developments

MacAndrews & Forbes Seeks Strategic Options For Revlon
Jan 15 16
Revlon, Inc. (NYSE:REV) controlling shareholder MacAndrews & Forbes Holdings, Inc., said it would seek strategic alternatives for Revlon but did not detail a specific plan. MacAndrews & Forbes, which has a 77.6% stake in Revlon said it did not have any specific or definitive plan or proposal.


