MacAndrews & Forbes Holdings Inc.






Tags:
 
Hart-Scott-Rodino Act (HSR) 

Competition 

 


      Last Updated:
    

July 1, 2013 

United States of America, Plaintiff v. MacAndrews & Forbes Holdings Inc., Defendant. 

      FTC Matter/File Number:
    

        121 0203      



      Civil Action Number:
    

        113-cv-00926      



      Enforcement Type:
    

        Civil Penalty (7a)      



      Federal Court:
    

        District of Columbia      



Case Timeline







July 1, 2013 


 Final Judgment (96.11 KB)









June 20, 2013 


 Complaint for Civil Penalties for Failure to Comply with the Premerger Reporting and Waiting Requirements of the Hart-Scott-Rodino Act (1.9 MB)
 Plaintiffs Motion for Entry of Final Judgment (36.85 KB)
 Joint Stipulation (383.36 KB)
 Final Judgment (47.71 KB)



PRESS RELEASE: Investment Firm of MacAndrews & Forbes to Pay $720,000 Penalty to Resolve FTC Allegations Related to Premerger Filing Requirements 
















